name: Open Donation
description:
Get Real Charleston is a non profit company that hosts events, parties and fundraisers for local charities here in Charleston, SC.  We have two great interns that do great work for us and help spread the concept of philithropy to a younger demographic.  Any donation made will help us advertise and host better events.  

Thank you in advance for your donation and as always it is tax deductable!
